            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " your taxes already paid to build and maintain. This would include the extremely unpopular proposition of per-mile driving fees as well as the even more creative road usage fees. Why politicians are determined to die on this hill is a mystery, but we might want to oblige them on that.",
            "type": "text",
