            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", whether you live in a rural or urban area, and other factors. A third-party entity will enforce these taxes, which no doubt will be one or more big tech companies since they are experts at tracking people and invading their privacy. Adding insult to injury, there will be a propaganda ad campaign to get the public excited.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Now here’s the real kicker: the bill spells out how there will be advisory boards that will study all these extra ways you’ll be nickeled and dimed for driving. Those boards are required to include “advocacy groups focused on equity.”",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
