          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " will be requirements in this bill for all new vehicles to be outfitted with “advanced drunk and impaired driving prevention technology” through the establishment of a new safety standard. News flash: much of the increased cost of cars these days ",
