            "direction": "ltr",
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "__GHOST_URL__/articles/features-3/analog-making-comeback/",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". Oddly, road fatalities have increased in recent years, almost like the government regulations aren’t working. Oh, but this one will. I can imagine this plan will entail putting breathalyzers into all new cars, as well as driver-monitoring systems which will decide on the spot if you’re too buzzed to be behind the wheel.",
